<h2>Folding Glass Walls</h2>
Folding glass walls are a signature product of Solar Innovations<sup>¬Æ</sup>. The industry also calls them bi-fold doors or accordion style doors. These doors accommodate any number of panels in addition to configurations. Solar Innovations<sup>¬Æ</sup> provides in-folding and out-folding glass walls thus accommodating the needs of many applications. Swing doors (also known as man doors) can be integrated into the folding glass walls. This allows the user to quickly enter and exit a room without operating all the panels.¬†Folding glass walls are engineered by Solar's in-house engineers¬†to allow high DP ratings and ensure they withstand extreme circumstances.

These walls provide flexibility and span larger openings than traditional doors, providing seamless transitions between structures and the outdoors. Folding glass wall systems can, in addition, be used for any number of applications. Some of these applications include stadiums, hospitals, hotels, and other applications.[/vc_column_text][/vc_column][vc_column width="2/3"][vc_single_image image="36828" img_size="full" alignment="right"][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row][vc_column width="1/2"][vc_column_text]<a href="/our-products/aluminum-doors/folding-glass-walls/commercial-folding-glass-walls/"><img class="alignnone wp-image-36797 size-full" src="https://solarinnovations.com/wp-content/uploads/nike-folding-glass-wall2.png" alt="Commercial Aluminum Folding Glass Walls or bi-fold doors" width="680" height="380" /></a>
<h2><a href="/our-products/aluminum-doors/folding-glass-walls/commercial-folding-glass-walls/">COMMERCIAL FOLDING GLASS WALLS</a></h2>
As an American manufacturer that specializes in custom folding glass wall systems, Solar Innovations<sup>¬Æ</sup> is ideal for commercial glazing solutions. In addition, Solar creates folding glass walls that are completely customizable.¬† Solar‚Äôs <a href="/information/specifications-2/">specifications</a> simplify the process of incorporating Solar‚Äôs products. It is impossible to mention every product application or configuration because there are simply so many.

Commercial hardware options include single and double door panic hardware, corrosion-proof two-point locks, ADA compliant sills, high-performance sills for high wind and water applications, as well as door catches and closers. Solar also has a ten-inch bottom rail available for ADA compliancy if needed.[/vc_column_text][/vc_column][vc_column width="1/2"][vc_column_text]<a href="/our-products/aluminum-doors/folding-glass-walls/residential-folding-glass-walls/"><img class="alignnone wp-image-36802 size-full" src="https://solarinnovations.com/wp-content/uploads/residential-folding-glass-doors-riverside.png" alt="Amy Schumers penthouse with bi-fold doors" width="680" height="380" /></a>
<h2><a href="/our-products/aluminum-doors/folding-glass-walls/residential-folding-glass-walls/">RESIDENTIAL GLASS WALLS</a></h2>
<div id="wrapper">
<div id="main">
<div class="main-holder">
<div id="content">
<div class="content-block">

Residential folding glass walls can virtually be anywhere in a home. These glass partitions can be used for exterior applications, where there will be contact with wind and water. We also use them as interior operable partition applications where there is no contact with the elements. This system can be fitted into pool enclosures, garages, and sheds. When the glass partition is open, you are presented with ample space for a lawn mower or car to pass. You can add an operable panel into the unit, depending on the configuration of the doors. This door allows you to pass through one panel, like a terrace door, instead of opening the entire unit.

If you desire the functionality of the folding glass wall system, but have concerns about insects, add a Screen System.

