<h2>G3 XTRA NARROW FOLDING GLASS WALL (MARINE/STOP GLAZE)</h2>
In our contemporary world, architects, homeowners, and business owners desire expansive windows and doors with minimal framing obstructing the view. Our marine glazed folding glass wall systems span large openings and provide seamless transitions. Even while closed, its narrow vertical frame maximizes views, reducing framing members and creating a clearer view.

Our patent design for the marine and stop glazing system combines vertical marine glazing with horizontal stop glazing. As a result, creating a narrower vertical frame than conventional stop glazed doors. The high-performance marine and stop glazing system by Solar Innovations&lt;sup&gt;¬Æ&lt;/sup&gt; has the narrowest four-sided glazed door. Now available for pivoting, stacking, swinging, and folding door units.

In a marine glazed system, the glass extends into the left and right framing members, eliminating the need for glass stops at the vertical frames. The hybrid marine and stop unit is structurally glazed within the glazing pocket.[/vc_column_text][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row][vc_column width="1/2"][vc_column_text]<img class="alignleft wp-image-36891 size-full" src="https://solarinnovations.com/wp-content/uploads/folding-glass-door-isos-2.gif" alt="" width="344" height="317" />
<h2><a href="/glazing/">Glazing Options</a></h2>
Creating the perfect environment for your home can be a complicated task.¬†Ensure your project looks and feels like the unique design parameters of your home, Solar Innovations<sup>¬Æ</sup> offers many glazing options. Your glass can be acid etched, frosted, art glass, or contain applied grids with multiple pattern options.

LowE Glazing helps maintain temperature,¬†energy consumption, and reduce the natural fading process the sun has on furniture and windows.[/vc_column_text][/vc_column][vc_column width="1/2"][vc_column_text]<code>[video_lightbox_youtube video_id="hO4C2kgp-I4" width="679" height="403" anchor="https://solarinnovations.com/wp-content/uploads/FGW-Video.png"  alt="Folding Glass Walls"]</code>[/vc_column_text][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row][vc_column][vc_tta_tabs style="flat" shape="square" active_section="1"][vc_tta_section i_icon_fontawesome="fa fa-info-circle" add_icon="true" title="Product Overview" tab_id="1502111154780-fc435057-69ec"][vc_column_text]<a href="https://solarinnovations.com/wp-content/uploads/SI3000-Folding-Glass-Wall-Cut-Sheet-2.pdf"><img class="alignright wp-image-25556 size-full" src="https://solarinnovations.com/wp-content/uploads/coverpage1.png" alt="coverpage1" width="400" height="248" /></a>

Series SI3000 thermally enhanced aluminum folding glass wall systems are a great way to open your environment. They have been incorporated into pool houses, restaurants, retirement homes, stadiums, hotels, and golf resorts, just to name a few.

